data.title: "Bigg Boss" Rahul Mahajan goes home (TV Episode 2015)
data.meta_description: Rahul Mahajan goes home: With Gautam Gulati, Farah Khan, Mallika Sherawat, Pritam Singh. Farah welcomes Mallika Sherawat as special guest on the show. She is there to promote her film 'Dirty Politics'. After visiting the Bigg Boss house Mallika claims that except Gautam everybody else is a fake. It's time for eviction and between Dimpy and Rahul, Rahul gets booted from the house.
